8.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvY5MAw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvY5MAw.gif&h=652e83c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvY5MAw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvY5MAw.gif&h=652e83c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd0bb811bffc03d2db280355fd21adcb7660a840","tid":2380202,"uid":55257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Lx0Ooh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Lx0Ooh.jpg&h=4077e8a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8573793493c31e1eb8bead7533f46130d32a6cd","tid":2380202,"uid":55257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:01:29.000Z","msg":"1841年，是什麼概念？<br />\n<br />\n美國立國僅65年。林肯時年31歲，合夥開辦律師行，還未晉身眾議院。<br />\n維多利亞女王時年21歲，即位未足4年。成為印度女皇，是36年後的事。<br />\n李鴻章年僅17歲，正在攻讀經書考取功名。洋務運動，是20年後的事。<br />\n坂本龍馬剛滿5歲，被笑是鼻涕蟲。明治維新，是27年後的事。<br />\n<br />\n大清被打敗這件事，本身就震憾東亞秩序。<br />\n英吉利逐步邁向日不落，列強陸續而來，東亞醞釀巨變。<br />\n<br />\n〈香港開埠180周年紀念〉全文閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.watershedhk.com/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e9%96%8b%e5%9f%a0180%e5%91%a8%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%80%e5%bf%b5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com%2F%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2596%258b%25e5%259f%25a0180%25e5%2591%25a8%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e7%25b4%2580%25e5%25bf%25b5%2F&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=fbef9228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.watershedhk.com/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e9%96%8b%e5%9f%a0180%e5%91%a8%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%80%e5%bf%b5/</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkwatershed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkwatershed&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=7f45506f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkwatershed</a><br />\nMeWe: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/watershedhongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fwatershedhongkong&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=a1e63d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/watershedhongkong</a><br />\nWeb: <a href=\"https://www.watershedhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watershedhk.com&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=c1a83f37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.watershedhk.com</a><br />\n<br />\n█ 支持WatershedHK運作以及尊屬分享：<br />\nPatreon: <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/WatershedHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2FWatershedHK&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=ea950835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/WatershedHK</a>"},{"pid":"b0a018a6a19b23805fce3560a62295c09258eb35","tid":2380202,"uid":55257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T01:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrEFOoK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrEFOoK.jpg&h=216091e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2QmxQq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2QmxQq.jpg&h=e636c1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHYZ3W6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHYZ3W6.jpg&h=316a8175&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVEuGJ